author: Source: Western Telegraph
title: Slaven Bilic lauds "brilliant" Jose Mourinho ahead of West Ham v Chelsea - Western Telegraph
text:
The Portuguese finds himself under scrutiny following Chelsea's poor start to the season, with the reigning champions down in 12th place after just three wins from their opening nine games. West Ham, by contrast, are flying high in fourth spot after a sparkling start to Bilic's reign at Upton Park.
 Western Telegraph.
